## Architecture

This is a multi-platform monorepo containing:

{% if "backend" in platforms %}- **backend/** - Spring Boot 4 (Kotlin) REST API -> Azure Container Apps
{% endif %}{% if "user-web-app" in platforms %}- **user-web-app/** - Next.js user-facing web app (TypeScript) -> Cloudflare via OpenNext
{% endif %}{% if "admin-web-portal" in platforms %}- **admin-web-portal/** - Next.js admin web portal (TypeScript) -> Cloudflare via OpenNext
{% endif %}{% if "android" in platforms %}- **android/** - Android app (Kotlin/Jetpack Compose, MVVM)
{% endif %}{% if "ios" in platforms %}- **ios/** - iOS app (Swift/SwiftUI, MVVM)
{% endif %}
## Quick Start

```bash
# 1. Set up environment
{% if "backend" in platforms %}cp .env.example .env
{% endif %}{% if "user-web-app" in platforms %}cp user-web-app/.env.example user-web-app/.env.local
{% endif %}{% if "admin-web-portal" in platforms %}cp admin-web-portal/.env.example admin-web-portal/.env.local
{% endif %}
# Edit the copied env files with your {% if "backend" in platforms %}backend{% if "user-web-app" in platforms or "admin-web-portal" in platforms %} and {% endif %}{% endif %}{% if "user-web-app" in platforms or "admin-web-portal" in platforms %}web app{% endif %} credentials

# 2. Generate API clients from OpenAPI spec
task generate-clients
{% if use_docker %}
# 3. Start local services
docker compose up -d
{% endif %}{% if "backend" in platforms %}
# 4. Start backend
task backend:run
{% endif %}{% if "user-web-app" in platforms %}
# 5. Start the user web app
task user-web-app:dev
{% endif %}{% if "admin-web-portal" in platforms %}
# 6. Start the admin web portal
task admin-web-portal:dev
{% endif %}
```

